{"tid":1473024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夢醒左之後覺得好攰 好無動力","createTime":"2019-08-14T17:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T11:27:54.000Z","uid":224591,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d19b5db0de9f3a112360ba98832d7e0bc7d72e","tid":1473024,"uid":224591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"第一次開post, 請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說自從612之後都一直keep住有發夢, 去到最近更加會去前線, 食下tg咁<br />\n但去到呢幾個星期開始出現有問題, 慢慢開始咳, 腸胃唔舒服<br />\n本身覺得無咩野既, 大把人都係咁<br />\n點知發夢發到811,812之後, 嚴重左, 咳係嚴重左, 但都接受到<br />\n到左尋日, 腸胃好唔舒服, 但又唔覺得痛, 有種囉囉攣既感覺, 做野無曬心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提唔起勁, 機又唔想打, 同fd見面又無曬心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到左今日, 直頭覺得好似人生無曬目標咁, 無曬生存意義<br />\n咩都唔想做, 好攰好攰, 心情好差, 個人好空洞<br />\n晏就仲呆坐左兩個鐘, 自己都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想搵人傾下計, 發泄下<br />\n好想快d到818, 好想搵d有意義既野做<br />\n第一次咁想發夢, 我係咪已經無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到呢一刻, 都仲係有一樣既感覺, 可以做d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548537192ae5a393aeffcb347a363d1cd30e6888","tid":1473024,"uid":224591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:35:42.000Z","msg":"唔知大家係咪都係咁<br />\n定係我自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3750ec4c8c08f35f9ed6c27808ed56997740cf51","tid":1473024,"uid":130421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14